window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I'm the new owner of a magical mansion.</b></p> <p>This mansion, well, it's not your typical building. It's a dungeon from another world, masquerading as just another private residence in the suburbs. It has enchanted rooms, can craft powerful items, build lethal traps, and produce incredible monsters.</p> <p>And it's my mission to protect and evolve its monstrous inhabitants.</p>"; 
